Preconditions:
- The input array `strength` is not null.
- The length of the input array `strength` is greater than 0.
- The elements in the input array `strength` are positive integers.

Postconditions:
- The method returns an integer value.
- The returned value is the sum of the total strengths of all contiguous groups of wizards.
- The returned value is modulo 10^9 + 7.